      "body": "resolve_repossession_conflicts has been dead since 7262b98d3e moved repossession-conflict handling to CompUnit::RepositoryRegistry. Both frontends and the legacy World wire that class's resolver; nothing calls this leftover copy. It also carried a stray-semicolon bug and an \"XXX typecheck??\". Drop it.\r\n\r\nregister_absolute_path_func has no callers, so $absolute_path_func is never set and absolute_path is already an identity function. Drop the unused hook and reduce absolute_path to a passthrough.",
